title: Blueshift - Wounded Man (ft. Blackalicious emcee Gift of Gab) -
description:
A single released on iTunes in 2012 by Blueshift, an independent rock band from Santa Rosa, CA. It features one of their favorite artists, Gift of Gab from Blackalicious. Blueshift released the track here on The Pirate Bay for free more than a year later, in an effort to gain some exposure for the band. 
     
     If you like what you hear, please show this little known band some support by liking their facebook page, following them on twitter, reverbnation, buying one of their other songs on ITunes, watching their youtube videos, listening to their Pandora channel, or any other number of actions you can be directed to from links on their website: 

www.blueshiftmusic.com
